Vondell Darr https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vondell_Darr 0 Vondell Darr Wilson (April 18, 1919 – September 10, 2012) was an American actress. She was born in Los Angeles. She achieved success in the late 1920s as a child actor and later played bit parts in her adult years. Her last role was in The Chocolate Soldier in 1941. Darr died on September 10, 2012.
